Name: File Copy and Move Tool
Description: A tool to copy or move a file from one location to another. It supports copying the file to a new location or moving (cutting and pasting) the file to a new location.
Param: action: The action to perform. Use "copy" to duplicate the file or "move" to relocate the file. One of these is required.
Param: source_path: The full path to the source file.
Param: destination_path: The full path to the destination location.

#!/usr/bin/env python3 ${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/file_copy_move.py
